21... Bxc3 22. Qxc3 Rxe4 23. Bd4
{ To be very honest, I tend to overestimate such beautiful one-sided positions, but I do believe that White has very good chances to make something out of this.  Our bishop has a brighter future and our queenside pawn structure is somewhat superior as well. A solid plus equal, as we say. }
